    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/4b3d78b0e228a89bcf45fba7cb760b6d.poster.avif?t=1722267477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/4b3d78b0e228a89bcf45fba7cb760b6d.webm?t=1722267477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/4b3d78b0e228a89bcf45fba7cb760b6d.mp4?t=1722267477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Happy Souls</strong> 是一款引人入胜的动作类类银河恶魔城游戏，结合了经典塞尔达风格谜题的元素。游戏跨越两个独特的世界，玩家必须通过复杂的谜题，避开可怕的陷阱，并与雄伟的敌人战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/f43513b3194184f02673913dd09a63c8.poster.avif?t=1722267477\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/f43513b3194184f02673913dd09a63c8.webm?t=1722267477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028300/extras/f43513b3194184f02673913dd09a63c8.mp4?t=1722267477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >双世界:</h2> 在两个不同的世界之间穿越，每个世界都有其独特的挑战和环境。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性的谜题:</h2> 解决各种受经典塞尔达游戏启发的谜题，以在游戏中取得进展。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的敌人:</h2> 面对强大的敌人和需要技能和策略才能击败的老板。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钥匙收集:</h2> 寻找并收集钥匙，以解锁新区域并在游戏中取得进展。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史诗般的故事情节:</h2> 开始一个任务，以击败潜伏在地狱深处的巨大黑暗邪恶，具有引人入胜的故事情节，让您保持参与感。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
